{"tid":2488329,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梅根據報準備好「原諒」皇室 但不出席喪禮是免成大眾焦點","createTime":"2021-04-14T07:13:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T07:20:03.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cf7450bc20dd01802420f3a03d3aeb1eb5f3a300","tid":2488329,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:13:45.000Z","msg":"英國皇夫菲臘親王逝世，身在美國的哈里王子將會返英出席祖父葬禮，其妻梅根則因懷孕聽從醫生意見不隨行。有梅根友人爆料指，梅根已「準備好原諒皇室家庭」，但她仍選擇留在加州，是不想在葬禮成為大眾焦點，並認為此行是哈里跟父親皇儲查理斯和兄長威廉王子修補關係的時機，「她不需要在場」。另據報哈里夫婦在菲臘親王辭世後曾經接觸英女皇，獲對方表示「理解」梅根不能出席。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210414/HHQWE4HFPNEI7BILJYADUNAGBE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210414%2FHHQWE4HFPNEI7BILJYADUNAGBE%2F&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1Tvbkzvjbcp9x5SJfJ3tUQBIbvNjo%3D&h=0d625d09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210414%2FHHQWE4HFPNEI7BILJYADUNAGBE%2F&h=e5f13e11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210414/HHQWE4HFPNEI7BILJYADUNAGBE/</a>"},{"pid":"34615c2b735f481a6bd46195bfbb5b5c9557f0d3","tid":2488329,"uid":357030,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:14:29.000Z","msg":"邊個要你原諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1df4b66fb15bdfab5db05c06391d1af3a5506e7","tid":2488329,"uid":4564,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:14:48.000Z","msg":"但王室唔打算原諒你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1640519b0b8b0d8624f0c2d7de9f1225a246f6f3","tid":2488329,"uid":66324,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedB